title: TNIAAM Reacts : Will you be going to the Syracuse Orange football spring game ? - Troy Nunes Is An Absolute Magician
body_text:
Welcome to SB Nation Reacts, a survey of fans across the NCAA. Throughout the year we ask questions of the most plugged-in Syracuse Orange fans and fans across the country.
Sign up here to participate in the weekly emailed surveys.
TNIAAM Reacts: Will you be going to the Syracuse football spring game?
And can the women’s lax team stay at #1?
Here’s this week’s survey questions for you to answer. We only have three this week because we know you are still recovering from four days of NCAA Tournament action.
Do you believe that Syracuse women’s lacrosse can hold up through the regular season?
Will Adrian Autry be at risk of losing other players to the transfer portal or will the exodus end with Symir Torrence and Jon Bol Ajak?
Spring football practice has started so we want to know if you plan on attending the spring game on April 21st. Would you be interested in a TNIAAM meet-up before the game?
